### Create a valid measurable habit

POST localhost:30000/api/v1/habits/measurable
Authorization: Bearer {{loginToken}}

{
    "label":"Walk 10k",
    "icon":4,
    "step":0.5,
    "unit":"km"
}

###

### Reject a measurable habit with domain validation errors

POST localhost:30000/api/v1/habits/measurable
Authorization: Bearer {{loginToken}}

{
    "label":"@",
    "icon":99,
    "step":0,
    "unit":"Kg!"
}
